dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.globaltime

Interface IGlobalTimeGateway

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable

    public interface IGlobalTimeGateway
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IGlobalTimeGateway: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This represents the ability to define a time gateway for establishing a global time domain over several communication clusters.
